{"id":391673873,"lang":"cpp","time":"11Â months","timestamp":1599366207,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"76 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/391673873/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"8.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        std::map<int,int> lastOccurence;\n        for (auto ch : s){\n            lastOccurence[ch] = -1;\n        }\n        auto maxLen = 0;\n        auto curLen = 0;\n        auto startInd = 0;\n        auto curInd = 0;\n\n        for (auto ch : s){\n            if (lastOccurence[ch] >= startInd){\n                startInd = lastOccurence[ch] + 1;\n            }\n            else {\n                curLen = curInd - startInd + 1 ;\n                maxLen = std::max(maxLen, curLen);\n            }\n            lastOccurence[ch] = curInd;\n            curInd += 1 ;\n        }\n        return maxLen;\n\n\n    }\n};\n","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
